<lb n="0679a11" ed="X"/><lb n="0480b05" ed="R089"/><cb:juan n="1" fun="close"><cb:jhead>大佛頂首楞嚴經截流卷上</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>